title: DIOR ReflectedDP S6D
description: Refined and contemporary, Dior continues to challenge the trend in the Clothes industry. Owning a pair means having a powerful fashion tool.

title: Mr Leight Runyon
description: The frame's design was inspired by classic silhouettes and the acetate styles of Old Hollywood. Its subtle cat eye shape, precious metal plating and precious metal lenses reflect the sophisticated lifestyles of Runyon Canyon's residents.

title: RetroSuperFuture Meta
description: Meta is a sleek all-metal silhouette characterized by a unique construction and streamlined angular design. The sharp geometric lenses are encapsulated inside the metal frame that circumnavigates and defines the shape. This version of Meta features grey lenses and silver metal finish.

title: Parasite Aerial
description: Parasite has revolutionized the Clothes industry with its introduction of the active “Stereo” System in 2002. Since then, the brand, still independent, has positioned itself as a leader of design and innovation.
